{"tid":2315423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女生與警拉扯5秒被控阻差辦公 控方三度研究直播新聞片段 律政司最終堅持起訴","createTime":"2020-12-07T07:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T14:23:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"17ae04fc46897a941222939936fb999babcce67f","tid":2315423,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T07:37:35.000Z","msg":"去年11月網民連續四日發動「三罷」，其間20歲大學女生被指在將軍澳港鐵站阻礙警員執法，被控阻差辦公罪。案件今日在觀塘裁判法院開審。控方開庭前看過辯方一段準備呈堂的新聞片段後，三度申請押後以索取律政司意見，指片段或影響檢控立場。惟最終律政司決定繼續起訴。案中警員指當日接報指有人破壞將軍澳站，到場追趕一名女子，其間女被告「突然出現」拉住女子，並與警員拉扯5秒。其後兩女均被警員制服。辯方則指警員混亂了兩人的身份。<br />\n<br />\n控方外聘大律師今日甫開庭便兩度申請押後案件，稱與辯方商討同意案情，並需觀看辯方提供的片段。主控並指，與案件主管討論後，需要把片段交給律政司索取意見。<br />\n<br />\n其後主控申請第三度押後。裁判官莫子聰聞言指案件只排期一天審訊，建議應先開始審訊，待有其他爭議時才在審訊階段提出。惟主控則稱，因片段拍到案件「最重要那一刻」，律政司看過後對案件有進一步分析，並稱或會影響繼續檢控的立場。惟其後再開庭時，主控稱索取律政司意見後決定繼續檢控。案件隨即開審。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201207/ILVDOCTUCZHRDAV353XU2KAJJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201207%2FILVDOCTUCZHRDAV353XU2KAJJM%2F&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=ed1e588c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201207%2FILVDOCTUCZHRDAV353XU2KAJJM%2F&h=313f9398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201207/ILVDOCTUCZHRDAV353XU2KAJJM/</a>"},{"pid":"8aa87ba7bf055a5fc17736b8567f69ddb83e1d69","tid":2315423,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T07:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c230ac277c2c2548d8d6862e66b2949d0f5e17de","tid":2315423,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48de20c6b09fc30295aad6282a1198d8400dec1","tid":2315423,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cf2fb1c8b77e0023cb5c895cea590b33a0ece9","tid":2315423,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T09:21:57.000Z","msg":"辯方質疑當時多人圍住女子，是「人多拉人少」。張不同意，稱「我上前先，其他同事之後（上前），咁多人係假象」。辯方又指被告從沒有拉扯過金髮女子手臂，而從片段所見，張的制服過程只是 3 至 4 秒，非張所指拉扯了 5 至 6 秒。張不同意稱「當時我感覺到係 5 至 6 秒」。案件下午續審。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/11-14-%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%B7-20-%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8C%87%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E6%89%AF%E7%8A%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E8%87%82-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E8%AA%8D%E9%8C%AF%E4%BA%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-14-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25BD%25B7-20-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%2589%25AF%25E7%258A%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2587%2582-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%258C%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=83bf6c93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-14-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25BD%25B7-20-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25